title: SUPCASE iPhone X, iPhone XS Case, [Unicorn Beetle Style] Premium Hybrid Protective Clear Case for Apple iPhone X 2017/ iPhone XS 2018 Release (Black)
feature: Compatible with Apple iPhone X (2017) / iPhone XS 2018. Not for Apple iPhone 8/8 Plus.
Slim, minimalist profile makes it easy to slip smartphone in and out of pockets and bags
Bumpers constructed of shock-absorbent TPU materials; PC backing prevents scratches and blemishes
Precise cutouts ensure full access to iPhone ports, functions and features
Elevated bezel ensures screen and camera lens avoid contact with surfaces
description: The Unicorn Beetle Style combines an attractive, minimalist design with the reliable drop protection that we have come to expect from the UB Family. Equipped with a shock-absorbent, wraparound TPU bumper, this case not only protects the edges of your iPhone X, but also the fragile body of your smartphone. A clear back panel prevents scratches, while raised edges along the bumper keep your screen and camera lenses from touching surfaces.
